        {
            "title": "特朗普支持的候選人贏得宏都拉斯總統大選",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 經過漫長而混亂的計票過程之後，宏都拉斯總統大選終於宣布一位保守派候選人獲勝，這位候選人得到美國總統特朗普的支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">選舉當局周三宣布，納斯裡·「蒂托」·阿斯富拉贏得了11月30日的選舉，他以微弱優勢擊敗了電視名人薩爾瓦多·納斯魯拉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據選舉機構網站公佈的最新計票結果，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿斯富拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿斯富拉\">阿斯富拉</a>獲得40.3%的選票，納斯魯拉獲得39.5%的選票。執政黨候選人裡克西·蒙卡達位列第三，得票19.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">選舉機構花了三周多的時間才宣布結果，在此期間，納斯魯拉和蒙卡達都指控選舉存在舞弊行為。結果公佈之後，納斯魯拉已表示不會承認敗選，將通過合法、和平方式「捍衛」選舉。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5b543dc9-1c98-3e09-b569-aa2330837652-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">結果在聖誕前日下午公佈，許多宏都拉斯人正在與家人團聚，因此短期內發生動亂的可能性不大。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">67歲的阿斯富拉曾承諾切斷與北京和委內瑞拉的關係，並與「友邦三角」——美國、台灣和以色列——建立密切關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務卿馬爾科·盧比奧迅速向阿斯富拉表示祝賀，他在X上發帖稱，美國「期待與他的政府合作，促進我們半球的繁榮與安全」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"納斯裡·阿斯富拉攝影：Tomas Ayuso/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CICum5I1Qprsg6GpfhWIag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e8a25ea423d13be193d2f6636602c44a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">納斯裡·阿斯富拉攝影：Tomas Ayuso/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump-Backed Construction Magnate Wins Honduras Election (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Jose Orozco、Maya Averbuch.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%9A%84%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%8F%E5%BE%97%E5%AE%8F%E9%83%BD%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-233829671.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-25 12:46:04",
