        },
        {
            "title": "國投瑞銀白銀期貨基金跌停 此前收緊申購規定並多次發布風險提示",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 周四中國唯一一只以白銀期貨為底層資產的基金跌停，結束了此前瘋狂的上漲行情，基金管理人此前罕見發布了一系列風險提示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著全球對貴金屬的興趣升溫，國投瑞銀白銀期貨證券投資基金(LOF)數周持續上漲，但基金管理人認為不具備可持續性。周三現貨白銀價格觸及每盎司72.70美元的紀錄高位，並有望創下自1979年以來最佳年度表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周該基金連續三天漲停後，國投瑞銀基金管理有限公司周三晚間收緊申購規定。根據其在網站發布的公告，該基金C類基金占有率申購限額自12月26日起調整為100元人民幣，A類申購限額仍為500元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b8d39c94-e737-345a-aa5b-2708592738b3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dakNxIJvSsX3QDkDM7FQNw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/da14e12e09d0672353f6878ce57000f8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基金管理人還再次發布基金占有率二級市場交易價格溢價風險提示，稱投資者如果盲目投資於高溢價率的基金占有率，可能面臨較大損失。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年以來，該白銀基金的漲幅已接近220%，而同期上海白銀期貨價格僅上漲約128%。截至周三，該基金相對於底層資產的溢價已接近62%，高於本月初的7%。隨著基金價格下跌和期貨價格繼續上漲，預計周四該溢價水平將有所回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國投瑞銀不予置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Silver Fund Plunges After String of Moves to Quell Frenzy</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%95%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E7%99%BD%E9%8A%80%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%B7%8C%E5%81%9C-%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E6%94%B6%E7%B7%8A%E7%94%B3%E8%B3%BC%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%A6%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA-082617405.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-25 17:05:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "泰自豪黨推舉外長為第二位泰國總理候選人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 泰國外交部長西哈薩·蓬集格已被選為泰自豪黨的第二位總理候選人，參加定於2月舉行的提前大選。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為泰黨周三晚些時候發表的一份聲明表示，資深外交官西哈薩列名於黨魁暨現任總理阿努廷·參威拉軍之後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泰自豪黨副黨魁西裡蓬周三早些時候曾告訴記者，阿努廷將是唯一候選人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：周三，泰自豪黨推選阿努廷為本黨唯一總理候選人</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Thailand’s Bhumjaithai Party Picks Sihasak as Second PM Nominee</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-98e0a520-55f6-307b-ba66-1fab19f4fea5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
